Photo: sunset_from_apartment.jpg
Date: 2024-06-15
Description: A photo taken from my apartment window in Portland. The sky is pink and orange, fading into purple. The city skyline is silhouetted against the sunset. There's a feeling of peace in this image — the first time I felt like I'd made the right decision.
Tags: portland, sunset, new-beginning, peaceful

Photo: dnd_group.jpg
Date: 2024-07-20
Description: A group photo after our first D&D campaign. Four people around a table covered in dice, character sheets, and snacks. I'm laughing in the photo — genuinely laughing. Maya is next to me making bunny ears behind my head. This was the night I realized I had real friends here.
Tags: friends, dnd, portland, belonging

Photo: thanksgiving_dinner.jpg
Date: 2024-11-28
Description: A solo Thanksgiving setup. Small table with a mini turkey, mashed potatoes, cranberry sauce, and a single candle. A laptop in the background with a paused video call. It looks lonely but it wasn't — it was peaceful. Proof that you can be alone and still feel whole.
Tags: thanksgiving, solo, cooking, peaceful

Photo: portland_street.jpg
Date: 2024-09-03
Description: A rainy Portland street with colorful houses and autumn leaves. I took this during a morning walk. The air smells like coffee and wet leaves. I remember thinking: "I live here now. This is my city."
